    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter.gif\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14718\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter-300x300.gif?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter.gif?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter.gif?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter.gif?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/25-Must-Follow-NGO-Resources-on-Twitter.gif?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>A follow-up post to <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/09/10/five-online-fundraising-best-practices-for-small-ngos-in-developing-countries/\">Five Online Fundraising Best Practices for NGOs</a>\u00a0and <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/09/23/five-social-media-best-practices-for-small-ngos-in-developing-countries/\">Five Social Media Best Practices for NGOs</a>, below is a list of 25 resources that regularly tweet and retweet useful fundraising and social media advice and information valuable to NGOs worldwide, particularly those engaged in international development. By studying their tweets and utilizing the resources they advocate for, your NGO will become better equipped to inspire online donors and supporters and consequently\u00a0achieve your mission and programs.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. CIVICUS :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CIVICUSalliance\">@CIVICUSalliance</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/CIVICUSalliance\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14691 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"CIVICUS\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/CIVICUS.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/CIVICUS.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/CIVICUS.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Devex :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/devex\">@Devex</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/devex\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14697\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Devex\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Devex.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Devex.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Devex.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. FundsForNGOs :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fundsforngos\">@FundsForNGOs</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/fundsforngos\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14702\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Funds for NGOs\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Funds-for-NGOs.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Funds-for-NGOs.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Funds-for-NGOs.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Global Development ::\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GdnDevelopment\">@GdnDevelopment</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/GdnDevelopment\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Guardian Global Development\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Guardian-Global-Development.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Global Giving :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/globalgiving\">@GlobalGiving</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/globalgiving\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14694\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Global Giving\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Global-Giving.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Global-Giving.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Global-Giving.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Global Voices :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/globalvoices\">@GlobalVoices</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/globalvoices\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14682 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Global Voices\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgoo