></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. International Development Jobs ::\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/InDevJobs\">@InDevJobs</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/InDevJobs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"International Development Jobs\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/International-Development-Jobs.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Mashable SocialMedia :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mashsocialmedia\">@MashSocialMedia</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/mashsocialmedia\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14680 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Mashable Social Media\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mashable-Social-Media.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mashable-Social-Media.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Mashable-Social-Media.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Meedan :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/meedan\">@Meedan</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/meedan\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14689 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Meedan\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Meedan.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Meedan.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Meedan.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=