od.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NetSquared.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">15. NextBillion :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nextbillion\">@NextBillion</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nextbillion\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14673 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Next Billion\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Next-Billion.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Next-Billion.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Next-Billion.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">16. NGO Pulse SANGONeT :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SangoNet\">@SaingoNeT</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/SangoNet\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14659 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"NGO SangoNet\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NGO-SangoNet.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NGO-SangoNet.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NGO-SangoNet.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">17. NGO Source :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ngosource\">@NGOsource</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ngosource\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14657 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\"