9px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">20. Social BlaBla :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/socialblabla\">@SocialBlaBla</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/socialblabla\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14712\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"SocialBlaBla\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/SocialBlaBla.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/SocialBlaBla.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/SocialBlaBla.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">21. Souktel :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/souktel\">@Souktel</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/souktel\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14668 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Souktel\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Souktel.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Souktel.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Souktel.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">22. \u00a0Tech Change :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/techchange\">@TechChange</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/techchange\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14675 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Tech Change\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Tech-Change.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Tech-Change.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Tech-Change.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">23. UN Foundation :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/unfoundation\">@UNFoundation</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/unfoundation\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14671 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"UN Foundation\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/UN-Foundation.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/UN-Foundation.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/UN-Foundation.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">24. WITNESS :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/witnessorg/\">@WITNESSorg</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/witnessorg/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14711\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"WITNESS\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/WITNESS.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/WITNESS.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/WITNESS.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">25. World NGO Day :: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/worldngoday\">@WorldNGODay</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/worldngoday\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14661 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"World NGO DAy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/World-NGO-DAy.png?resize=469%2C77\" width=\"469\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/World-NGO-DAy.png?w=469&amp;ssl=1 469w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/World-NGO-DAy.png?resize=300%2C49&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
