      "rendered": "<p>A follow-up post to Five Online Fundraising Best Practices for NGOs\u00a0and Five Social Media Best Practices for NGOs, below is a list of 25 resources that regularly tweet and retweet useful fundraising and social media advice and information valuable to NGOs worldwide, particularly those engaged in international development. By studying their tweets and utilizing the resources they advocate for, your NGO will become better equipped to inspire online donors and supporters and consequently\u00a0achieve your mission and programs. 1. CIVICUS :: @CIVICUSalliance 2. Devex :: @Devex 3. FundsForNGOs :: @FundsForNGOs 4. Global Development ::\u00a0@GdnDevelopment 5. Global Giving :: @GlobalGiving 6. Global </p>\n",
